From Bijan Mobasseri Subject Re V V V V Vx We have seen lots of discussion on automobile engine configuration Let me ask a similar question from the aviation field You must have seen images of prop planes with all cylinders exposed I have seen up to cylinders positioned radially in a circular fashion with the prop at the center of the circle This arrangement always brings up a geometric dilemma How can one crankshaft throw accomodate rods or are the pistons displaced but not visible from the outside Bijan